"{\"uid\": \"mercurynews.com-2024-06-18-ralph-lauren-goes-with-basic-blue-jeans-for-team-usas-opening-olympic-ceremony-uniforms\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Today's e-Edition  Get Morning Report and other email newsletters    Get Morning Report and other email newsletters  Today's e-Edition  Trending:  By LEANNE ITALIE (AP Lifestyles Writer)  NEW YORK (AP) - WhenTeam USAwalks with the world's athletes at theParis Olympics'opening ceremony,they will be doing so in snappy tailored navy blazers from Ralph Lauren - and blue jeans.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 375, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 188, \"end\": 191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Next_Entertainment_World\", \"score\": 0.8660791024022668, \"rank\": 0.15460510694025967, \"text\": \"NEW\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Next_Entertainment_World\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Next_Entertainment_World\"}, {\"begin\": 192, \"end\": 196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/York\", \"score\": 0.9975018103394492, \"rank\": 0.002504444543588106, \"text\": \"YORK\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/York\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/York\"}, {\"begin\": 198, \"end\": 200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.197151086290432e-12, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 345, \"end\": 357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren_Corporation\", \"score\": 0.6609373523393215, \"rank\": 0.5130027020878518, \"text\": \"Ralph Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren_Corporation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just regular, everyday denim blue jeans.\", \"from\": 377, \"to\": 417, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ralph Lauren,which unveiled Tuesdayits ninth turncreatingOlympic parade looksfor the Americans, is billing the pairing as \\\"unexpected\\\" yet classic.\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 566, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 419, \"end\": 431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren_Corporation\", \"score\": 0.6609373523393215, \"rank\": 0.5130027020878518, \"text\": \"Ralph Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren_Corporation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"David Lauren,the company's chief branding and innovation officer and its founder's son, was unbothered by the casualness of blue denim.\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 703, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 568, \"end\": 580, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Lauren\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"David Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Lauren\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Lauren\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We work very closely with Team USA to make the athletes feel at once dressed up, feel like a team, but at the same time comfortable and very distinctively American,\\\" he told The Associated Press on Monday during a media preview at the company's posh New York headquarters.\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 978, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 732, \"end\": 740, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9992294559363246, \"rank\": 0.0007020382995300909, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 884, \"end\": 900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999999973083504, \"rank\": 2.691859405034611e-09, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 956, \"end\": 964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999943233888, \"rank\": 5.6511829801988935e-09, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Nothing says America like blue jeans, especially when we are in Paris,\\\" Lauren added.\", \"from\": 980, \"to\": 1066, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1045, \"end\": 1050, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.736762215058299e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And it gives the athletes a chance to feel a sense of a culture but also feel like themselves and what is natural.\\\"\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1183, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The single-breasted wool blazers come with red-and-white tipping worn with a blue-and-white striped Oxford shirt and cream suede buck lace-up shoes.\", \"from\": 1185, \"to\": 1333, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1285, \"end\": 1297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dress_shirt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Oxford shirt\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dress_shirt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dress_shirt\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The jeans, at least, are tapered.\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1367, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Oh, and there are neck ties, in blue.\", \"from\": 1368, \"to\": 1405, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For the closing ceremony, the team will wear sharp white, moto-style denim jeans with matching jackets designed in, yes, patriotic red, white and blue.\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1558, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The company gathered a few Paris-bound athletes to show off the parade uniformsfor the Summer Gamesthat begin next month in one ofthe world's fashion capitals.\", \"from\": 1560, \"to\": 1719, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Daniela Moroz, 23, is competing in sailingat her first Olympics.\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1785, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1721, \"end\": 1728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniela_Alves_Lima\", \"score\": 0.999996816498489, \"rank\": 2.958232593265409e-06, \"text\": \"Daniela\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniela_Alves_Lima\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniela_Alves_Lima\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She loved the racing details of the closing look she modeled, down to the shoes.\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1866, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The zip jackets have \\\"USA\\\" splashed across the front in huge letters, with \\\"Team USA\\\" in blue high on the outside seam of one pant leg.\", \"from\": 1867, \"to\": 2002, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Team caps are duck bill: The visor is in white, with red and blue details.\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2077, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am a racer on the water so that really speaks to me,\\\" said Moroz, born and raised in the San Francisco Bay Area, of the moto touches.\", \"from\": 2079, \"to\": 2215, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's super comfortable.\\\"\", \"from\": 2216, \"to\": 2241, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lauren called the closing ceremony looks \\\"more graphic, more fun, a little more exciting.\\\"\", \"from\": 2243, \"to\": 2333, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The company also designed Team USA gear available for sale starting Tuesday at RalphLauren.com, TeamUSAShop.com and company stores in the U.S. and France.\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2489, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2361, \"end\": 2369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9992294559363246, \"rank\": 0.0007020382995300909, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2482, \"end\": 2488, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.987181971336716, \"rank\": 0.012981859070884002, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Among the wares on offer are polo shirts made of 100% recycled cotton.\", \"from\": 2490, \"to\": 2560, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the first time Ralph Lauren has achieved thatlevel of sustainabilityin Olympic gear, David Lauren said.\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2669, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2581, \"end\": 2593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren_Corporation\", \"score\": 0.6609373523393215, \"rank\": 0.5130027020878518, \"text\": \"Ralph Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren_Corporation\"}, {\"begin\": 2651, \"end\": 2663, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Lauren\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"David Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Lauren\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Lauren\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some proceeds of retail sales go to help support U.S. athletes training for their Olympic moments.\", \"from\": 2671, \"to\": 2769, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lauren would not be more specific on how much money the company sends their way.\", \"from\": 2770, \"to\": 2850, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The opening and closing ceremony uniforms, the same for the Olympics andsubsequent Paralympics,were made in the U.S.\", \"from\": 2852, \"to\": 2968, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The gear on sale to the public was made in both the U.S. and other countries.\", \"from\": 2969, \"to\": 3046, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jamal Hill, a Paralympic swimmer who earned a bronze medal in Tokyo, is returning to compete in Paris at age 29.\", \"from\": 3048, \"to\": 3160, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3048, \"end\": 3053, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamal_Lyon\", \"score\": 0.9999999686433516, \"rank\": 3.1356425866263017e-08, \"text\": \"Jamal\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamal_Lyon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamal_Lyon\"}, {\"begin\": 3062, \"end\": 3080, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Para_swimming\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paralympic swimmer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Para_swimming\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Para_swimming\"}, {\"begin\": 3110, \"end\": 3115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9641079788347873, \"rank\": 0.03689485252228158, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 3144, \"end\": 3149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.736762215058299e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He thinks the uniforms will resonate with millennialsand Gen Z.\", \"from\": 3161, \"to\": 3224, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3218, \"end\": 3223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Generation_Z\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gen Z\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Generation_Z\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Generation_Z\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They have a really, really nice unique modern flair,\\\" said Hill, who grew up in Los Angeles.\", \"from\": 3226, \"to\": 3319, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3307, \"end\": 3318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999995766302, \"rank\": 4.0407644743630824e-10, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fencer Daryl Homer, 33,will be Paris as an alternate after he tore his Achilles tendon a month before qualification.\", \"from\": 3321, \"to\": 3437, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3328, \"end\": 3339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daryl_Homer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Daryl Homer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daryl_Homer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daryl_Homer\"}, {\"begin\": 3352, \"end\": 3357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.736762215058299e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3392, \"end\": 3400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\", \"score\": 0.9999774742709223, \"rank\": 2.2526236345674955e-05, \"text\": \"Achilles\", \"types\": [\"Q4936952\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's his fourth trip to the Olympics.\", \"from\": 3438, \"to\": 3475, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He earned a silver medal in 2016 in Rio de Janeiro.\", \"from\": 3476, \"to\": 3527, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3512, \"end\": 3526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.132695189600863e-17, \"text\": \"Rio de Janeiro\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Of the blue denim moment, Homer said: \\\"It's very modern, it's approachable.\", \"from\": 3529, \"to\": 3604, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3555, \"end\": 3560, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Homer_Simpson\", \"score\": 0.9999999998285602, \"rank\": 1.6940066323826687e-10, \"text\": \"Homer\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Homer_Simpson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Homer_Simpson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are going to be walking in Paris in the heat.\", \"from\": 3605, \"to\": 3653, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3635, \"end\": 3640, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.736762215058299e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a lighter look with a bit more room to move around.\\\"\", \"from\": 3654, \"to\": 3711, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kamren Larsen, a 24-year-oldBMX racerfrom Bakersfield, California, is headed to his first Olympics.\", \"from\": 3713, \"to\": 3812, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3755, \"end\": 3778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bakersfield,_California\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bakersfield, California\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bakersfield,_California\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bakersfield,_California\"}, {\"begin\": 3755, \"end\": 3778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bakersfield,_California\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bakersfield, California\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bakersfield,_California\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bakersfield,_California\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He thinks the crisp blazers with Oxford shirts balance out the more laid-back nature of the jeans.\", \"from\": 3813, \"to\": 3911, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think Ralph did a good job in diversifying,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3913, \"to\": 3969, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright \\u00a9 2025 MediaNews Group\", \"from\": 3971, \"to\": 4003, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3988, \"end\": 4003, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Digital_First_Media\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"MediaNews Group\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Digital_First_Media\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Digital_First_Media\"}]}]}"